# 📌 Key Takeaways

- AI is transforming both cyber defense and cyber attacks.
- Autonomous AI can now assist attackers in performing complex attack chains.
- Cyber Resilience is becoming more important than traditional prevention alone.
- Organizations must defend against AI-generated phishing, deepfakes, prompt injection, and data poisoning.
- Regular patch management, Zero Trust security, and AI governance are essential for modern cybersecurity.

